This paper deals with computer vision and image processing, which suggests that it is likely to belong to the Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV) sub-category. Additionally, the use of fuzzy logic and membership functions suggests that it may also belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also involves information retrieval and matching, which could place it in the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category. Finally, the use of image databases and testing suggests that it may also belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
